{"4065180": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Football Temptations", "steam_appid": 4065180, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏈 <strong>Football Temptations</strong> 是一款面向成人的視覺小說，融合了職業美式足球的劇情、浪漫、誘惑以及改變人生的選擇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你將扮演 <strong>James</strong>，一名潛力巨大的年輕美式足球運動員。今年春天，他的夢想開始成真：被 <strong>Philadelphia Hawks</strong> 選中，並簽下新秀合約。逆境之下，他成功進入了53人最終名單。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4065180/extras/02e645b4d39ac54cc75be558745e46ae.poster.avif?t=1774705259\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4065180/extras/02e645b4d39ac54cc75be558745e46ae.webm?t=1774705259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4065180/extras/02e645b4d39ac54cc75be558745e46ae.mp4?t=1774705259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但這只是開始。為了留在賽場上——甚至可能帶領球隊贏得Bowl——James必須迅速證明自己的實力。幾場糟糕的比賽，他可能會被裁掉；一整個優秀的賽季，他可能成為明星。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4065180/extras/9ffcfb6d4d11f1444dab57dfc6827ee8.poster.avif?t=1774705259\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4065180/extras/9ffcfb6d4d11f1444dab57dfc6827ee8.webm?t=1774705259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4065180/extras/9ffcfb6d4d11f1444dab57dfc6827ee8.mp4?t=1774705259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >場下的壓力同樣不減。名聲帶來關注，尤其是女性的注意。但誘惑可能成為危險的干擾——特別是沒有穩定關係支撐時。你的挑戰是平衡個人生活與職業野心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一個決定都至關重要。你如何應對新聞發布會，以及如何與隊友、球迷和女性互動，將直接影響你每場比賽的表現。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>勝利條件：</strong> 到賽季末，你的目標是贏得Bowl，並有一名女朋友陪伴。只完成其中一項視為「半勝利」，這意味著有時你需要犧牲幾場比賽來豐富個人生活。即便是冠軍，如果沒有與人分享，也會覺得空虛。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4065180/extras/eda4734b07e00aa57b447441c2f477db.poster.avif?t=1774705259\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4065180/extras/eda4734b07e00aa57b447441c2f477db.webm?t=1774705259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4065180/extras/eda4734b07e00aa57b447441c2f477db.mp4?t=1774705259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ <strong>特色</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >分支劇情與重要選擇 — 你的回答和行動會導致不同的路線和結局</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >存在 NTR（可選擇避開）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4065180/extras/1736db7975bccfdf03fc0774a7bedc85.poster.avif?t=1774705259\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4065180/extras/1736db7975bccfdf03fc0774a7bedc85.webm?t=1774705259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4065180/extras/1736db7975bccfdf03fc0774a7bedc85.mp4?t=1774705259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完整美式足球賽季 — 從常規賽到季後賽</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >運動模擬元素 — 新聞發布會、訓練、社群媒體與球迷反應</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >許多女性角色可結識並發展戀情</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與女性、球迷、隊友等的多種衝突情境</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多樣的性愛場景，涵蓋不同興趣和癖好</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多重結局 — 你可以贏得Bowl，也可能未能進入季後賽，根據選擇可與不同女友結局</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >比賽中的語音解說</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精美渲染與電影式敘事</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多樣化事件與場景 — 賭場、酒吧、餐廳等</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>立即加入願望清單！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏈 <strong>Football Temptations</strong> 是一款面向成人的視覺小說，融合了職業美式足球的劇情、浪漫、誘惑以及改變人生的選擇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你將扮演 <strong>James</strong>，一名潛力巨大的年輕美式足球運動員。今年春天，他的夢想開始成真：被 <strong>Philadelphia Hawks</strong> 選中，並簽下新秀合約。逆境之下，他成功進入了53人最終名單。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4065180/extras/02e645b4d39ac54cc75be558745e46ae.poster.avif?t=1774705259\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4065180/extras/02e645b4d39ac54cc75be558745e46ae.webm?t=1774705259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4065180/extras/02e645b4d39ac54cc75be558745e46ae.mp4?t=1774705259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但這只是開始。為了留在賽場上——甚至可能帶領球隊贏得Bowl——James必須迅速證明自己的實力。幾場糟糕的比賽，他可能會被裁掉；一整個優秀的賽季，他可能成為明星。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4065180/extras/9ffcfb6d4d11f1444dab57dfc6827ee8.poster.avif?t=1774705259\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4065180/extras/9ffcfb6d4d11f1444dab57dfc6827ee8.webm?t=1774705259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4065180/extras/9ffcfb6d4d11f1444dab57dfc6827ee8.mp4?t=1774705259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></s